{"tid":1162411,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本】慎入 今朝屎忽痕走去なか卯嗌咗呢個定食","createTime":"2019-05-20T00:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T22:01:19.000Z","uid":207951,"like":279,"dislike":369,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c434897d258839e0d022a6b67c18590a6ace52","tid":1162411,"uid":207951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"小弟開咗學個半月 平時夜晚剩係掛住食咖哩同拉麵 有人約去居酒屋就炸雞薯條送酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始痾屎唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去食嘢都盡量食啲有纖維嘅嘢 但都無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗緊有咩方法可以痾暢快啲 就諗住買個麒麟果食下<br />\n<br />\n點知已經唔係貴嘅問題 而係根本無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是把心一橫<br />\n<br />\n去なか卯嗌咗呢個定食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iO9d5vn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiO9d5vn.png&h=31da20b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n330羊 納豆秋葵定食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連個湯都有秋葵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n納豆就咁食無用 所以發咗啲納豆先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OirDxaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOirDxaQ.png&h=2f82f9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒落啲秋葵到再撈<br />\n<br />\n到呢兜都起潺嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQg3h6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQg3h6.png&h=bf76a5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加隻蛋落去（金黃色嘅日本蛋黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n冚上碗飯到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBvg3iH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBvg3iH.png&h=24795b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加木魚絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfWW3iS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfWW3iS.png&h=a28f38b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1fb5cbf7c512885fb49fdbd962a990d4328646","tid":1162411,"uid":247139,"like":84,"dislike":4,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好平<br />\n賣相唔差"},{"pid":"ac009cf346d2dd25daa42ffc2a3686d399df2b59","tid":1162411,"uid":40470,"like":402,"dislike":9,"score":393,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:34:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚多泡<br />\n<br />\n精蟲嘔吐鼻涕飯"},{"pid":"8d01f36d914cacbe1ec5b7ade2ecf69a237aed5a","tid":1162411,"uid":62841,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"屎撈飯？"},{"pid":"6602d6629075d1a13c68ee703c6009871e3cc4da","tid":1162411,"uid":43785,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:41:23.000Z","msg":"一定好臭"},{"pid":"1f3d77cfc38f3af3a70c92603db699599df78328","tid":1162411,"uid":191815,"like":82,"dislike":4,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:42:05.000Z","msg":"納豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3499bf023fd923a6b4c8836b4e0d8403f64ccdd9","tid":1162411,"uid":221132,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:45:53.000Z","msg":"想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd72e6a0e1ccf8