7f4244d2dc08662439eb8e8970ec4799f216edd","tid":1162411,"uid":143319,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAjBjOH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAjBjOH.jpg&h=98c44f01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e61cbe6891d1aad428a9aea2e74afbf69e34612","tid":1162411,"uid":34952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:18:32.000Z","msg":"納豆同秋葵都咁難食<br />\n仲要溝埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e58599864705ad703f8a84bcd737d99f97638fb","tid":1162411,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6c434897d258839e0d022a6b67c18590a6ace52","tid":1162411,"uid":207951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"小弟開咗學個半月 平時夜晚剩係掛住食咖哩同拉麵 有人約去居酒屋就炸雞薯條送酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始痾屎唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去食嘢都盡量食啲有纖維嘅嘢 但都無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗緊有咩方法可以痾暢快啲 就諗住買個麒麟果食下<br />\n<br />\n點知已經唔係貴嘅問題 而係根本無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是把心一橫<br />\n<br />\n去なか卯嗌咗呢個定食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iO9d5vn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiO9d5vn.png&h=31da20b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n330羊 納豆秋葵定食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連個湯都有秋葵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n納豆就咁食無用 所以發咗啲納豆先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OirDxaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOirDxaQ.png&h=2f82f9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒落啲秋葵到再撈<br />\n<br />\n到呢兜都起潺嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EQg3h6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EQg3h6.png&h=bf76a5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加隻蛋落去（金黃色嘅日本蛋黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n冚上碗飯到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBvg3iH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBvg3iH.png&h=24795b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加木魚絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfWW3iS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfWW3iS.png&h=a28f38b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"食多啲水溶性纖維同益生菌啦屌... Yogurt, 泡菜 洋蔥，滑子菇，蕎頭"},{"pid":"abfc765f8eb71309ce0dd52e742c72e6496b3b36","tid":1162411,"uid":98056,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得納豆幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去親都買黎食"},{"pid":"ea461faea9f3e3a3c7ae83f2b39e9428c3c954d7","tid":1162411,"uid":207951,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n估唔到咁撚有效<br />\n朝頭早搭電車返學又逼<br />\n忍屎忍屁忍足咁多個站<br />\n<br />\n卒之去到新宿轉車頂唔緊衝咗入廁所<br />\n啲括約肌已經無力夾實 十足十搽咗K